ute. Farmers have the option to retain their land or sell it at the new rates.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/ghaziabad-high-court-boosts-farmers-compensation-for-indirapuram-extension-land/125149424?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-22468/125149424.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}